data.description: Home is nestled on a large 1/2 acre lot w/ spectacular mountain views & no back neighbor! Located just minutes from the charming towns of Star & Middleton. Home boasts professionally manicured grounds w/ a fire pit and garden beds to enjoy evenings under the stars in your own quiet backyard. Gourmet kitchen is equipped w/ stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, sleek granite countertops & a spacious walk-in pantry- ideal for those who love to cook & entertain. The kitchen seamlessly opens to the living areas, creating an inviting flow. The expansive master suite features tiled floors, a deep soaker tub  & a separate walk-in shower. Split bedroom layout with doors on each end for privacy. Upstairs, another bedroom w/ a bathroom & cozy bonus room offers a perfect private space for guests or family members. Along w/ the 5 bedrooms & 3 baths is a bonus room, office & RV + boat & toy parking! Walk to the community pool, as well as picturesque ponds & trails!
